&lt;section typeof='http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide'&gt;
&lt;img src='http://ptsefton.com/2019/11/05/FAIR Repo - eResearch Presentation/Slide01.png' alt='FAIR Simple Scalable Static Research Data Repository
