&lt;p&gt;This is the &lt;a href="https://researchobject.github.io/ro-crate/"&gt;home page for RO-Crate&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;section typeof='http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide'&gt;
