&lt;p&gt;Thereâ€™s also machine readable data in JSON-LD format.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;section typeof='http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide'&gt;
