&lt;p&gt;The JSON-LD is designed to be easily consumed by programs that can do things with the data - and is compatible ith Googleâ€™s DataSet search.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr/&gt;
